data.description: *Owner Financing* Wow, move in ready 4 bed / 2.5 bath / 2 car garage contemporary home at 2145 sq ft. nestled in a cul-de-sac of Raintree Subdivision. Enjoy this turn-key home that features two living areas downstairs, oversized kitchen island and pantry, granite counters, and French doors that lead to a deck to oversee the large backyard with a view. Great sized master bedroom that leads to large bathroom with double vanity and large walk-in closet. Easy access to 1604/35/The Forum.
